terra.shell.utils.system

Class JSHProcesses

  • java.lang.Object
    • terra.shell.utils.system.JSHProcesses

  • public class JSHProcesses
extends java.lang.Object

    Process Management Class

    This class is the process management interface for all running processes within JSH. Any JProcess or extension of a JProcess should be routed through this class to allow for System management of processes
